## Conventions

- Always use `ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush`
- Standalone components by default
- `@Output` with `EventEmitter` — never emit in constructor
- Clean up subscriptions with `takeUntil(destroy$)`
- Use `ng-content` with `select` for named projection
- Computed getters for dynamic classes
